Running DE analysis over lineages per TP in bulk

DefaultAssay(seuset)
## [1] "sf"
TPs <- unique(seuset@meta.data$Timepoint)
TPs <- TPs[order(TPs, decreasing = FALSE)]
TPs
## [1] d4  d5  d8  d14
## 15 Levels: d4 < d5 < d7 < d8 < d9 < d10 < d11 < d12 < d13 < d14 < ... < m12
TPs <- TPs[!TPs %in% c("d4","d7","d10","d12","d18","d21")]
TPs
## [1] d5  d8  d14
## 15 Levels: d4 < d5 < d7 < d8 < d9 < d10 < d11 < d12 < d13 < d14 < ... < m12
lineages <- c("AM","VM")
DE_results_list <- list()
DE_results_TF_list <- list()
DE_results_SF_list <- list()
ident_var <- "Lineage_TP"
Idents(seuset) <- ident_var

## Run separately for d4 with shared between lineages, so d4 against all.
DE_d4 <- FindMarkers(seuset, ident.1 = "shared_d4", ident.2 = NULL, min.pct = min_pct_exp)
DE_d4 <- DE_d4[DE_d4$p_val_adj < pval_adj_tresh,]
# Order on LogFC
DE_d4 <- DE_d4[order(DE_d4$avg_log2FC, decreasing = TRUE),]
DE_results_list[["shared_d4"]] <- DE_d4
# Selecting TFs in the DE-gene lists
DE_d4_TF <- DE_d4[rownames(DE_d4) %in% tf_vector,]
DE_results_TF_list[["shared_d4"]] <- DE_d4_TF

write.csv(DE_d4, paste0("DE-genes_shared_d4_pct", min_pct_exp, ".csv"), quote = FALSE)
write.csv(DE_d4_TF, paste0("DE-TFs_shared_d4_pct", min_pct_exp, ".csv"), quote = FALSE)
for (tp in TPs){
  ident1 <- paste(lineages[1], tp, sep = "_")
  print(ident1)
  ident2 <- paste(lineages[2], tp, sep = "_")
  print(ident2)
  comparison_id <- paste0(ident1, "vs", ident2)
  DE_results <- FindMarkers(seuset, ident.1 = ident1, ident.2 = ident2, min.pct = min_pct_exp)
  DE_results <- DE_results[DE_results$p_val_adj < pval_adj_tresh,]
  # Order on LogFC
  DE_results <- DE_results[order(DE_results$avg_log2FC, decreasing = TRUE),]
  write.csv(DE_results, paste0("DE-genes_", comparison_id, "_pct", min_pct_exp, ".csv"), quote = FALSE)
  DE_results_list[[comparison_id]] <- DE_results
  # Selecting TFs in the DE-gene lists
  DE_results_TF <- DE_results[rownames(DE_results) %in% tf_vector,]
  write.csv(DE_results_TF, paste0("DE-TFs_", comparison_id, "_pct", min_pct_exp, ".csv"), quote = FALSE)
  DE_results_TF_list[[comparison_id]] <- DE_results_TF
  
  DoHeatmap(seuset, features = c(head(rownames(DE_results), n = 20), tail(rownames(DE_results), n = 20)), group.by = ident_var)
}

Plotting mean expressions of the RA gene subsets

sf_tp_means <- AverageExpression(seuset, assays = "sf", slot = "data", group.by = c("Timepoint", "Lineage"))

sf_tp_means <- sf_tp_means[[1]]
se <- function(x) sqrt(var(x) / length(x))
## Create a list object with means per TP per lineage, for the different RA subsets:
RA_means_list <- list()
RA_plotdf_list <- list()
ggplot_list <- list()

for (i in names(RA_targets_list)){
  goi_means <- data.frame()
  ## Select the subsets of genes:
  genes_of_interest <- RA_targets_list[[i]]
  
  ## Take the mean expression per TP per lineage, 
  ## and add to both lineages d4 as first value
  goi_means <- sf_tp_means[rownames(sf_tp_means) %in% genes_of_interest,]
  
  goi_shared_means <- data.frame(d4 = as.vector(goi_means[,grepl("shared", colnames(goi_means))]), row.names=rownames(goi_means))
  goi_means <- goi_means[,!grepl("shared", colnames(goi_means))]
  
  
  
  goi_VM <- goi_means[,!grepl("AM",colnames(goi_means))]
  goi_AM <- goi_means[,!grepl("VM",colnames(goi_means))]
  
  colnames(goi_VM) <- gsub("_VM","",colnames(goi_VM))
  colnames(goi_AM) <- gsub("_AM","",colnames(goi_AM))
  
  goi_VM <- cbind(goi_shared_means, goi_VM)
  goi_AM <- cbind(goi_shared_means, goi_AM)
  
  ## AM misses the d18, fill in:
  goi_VM <- data.frame(goi_VM)
  goi_AM <- cbind(goi_AM,data.frame("d18" = rep(NA, length(rownames(goi_AM)))))
  goi_AM <- goi_AM[,colnames(goi_VM)]
  identical(colnames(goi_AM),colnames(goi_VM))
  
  rownames(goi_AM) <- paste0("AM_",rownames(goi_AM))
  rownames(goi_VM) <- paste0("VM_",rownames(goi_VM))

  ## Transpose & Melt for easier plotting:
  df_lin_means <- t(rbind(goi_AM, goi_VM))
  
  RA_means_list[[i]] <- df_lin_means
  plotdf_means <- melt(df_lin_means)
  colnames(plotdf_means) <- c("Timepoint","Lineage","Expression")
  RA_plotdf_list[[i]] <- plotdf_means

  ## Generate mean and standard deviation / standard error
  plot_sdmeans <- plotdf_means %>%
    #gather(Timepoint, Lineage, Expression) %>%
    separate(Lineage, c("Lineage","Gene")) %>%
    group_by(Timepoint, Lineage) %>%
    summarise(mExpression = mean(Expression),sdExpression = se(Expression))
  
  plot_sdmeans <- plot_sdmeans[!is.na(plot_sdmeans$mExpression),]

  ## Storing boundaries of Standard deviation / Standard error in df
  plot_sdmeans$lower <- (plot_sdmeans$mExpression-plot_sdmeans$sdExpression)
  plot_sdmeans$upper <- (plot_sdmeans$mExpression+plot_sdmeans$sdExpression)
  
  #plot_sdmeans <- as_tibble(plot_sdmeans)
  
  
  # remove timepoint only present in VM:
  plot_sdmeans <- plot_sdmeans[!grepl("d18", plot_sdmeans$Timepoint),]
  RA_means_list[[i]] <- plot_sdmeans
  print(plot_sdmeans)
  
  eb <- aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill = Lineage)
  
  g1 <- ggplot(plot_sdmeans, aes(x=Timepoint, y = mExpression, color = Lineage, group = Lineage)) + 
  geom_line(aes(group = Lineage)) +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("darkred","darkblue")) + 
  geom_ribbon(eb, alpha=0.2) + 
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("red","blue")) +
  ggtitle(paste0("Expression of RA subset ",i)) +
  ylab("Mean Expression (SE)") + xlab("Timepoint in days")
  
  pdf(paste0("lineplot_means_standarderror_",i,".pdf"))
  print(g1)
  dev.off()
  
  ggplot_list[[i]] <- g1
}

  goi_AM <- goi_AM[,colnames(goi_VM)]
  identical(colnames(goi_AM),colnames(goi_VM))
  
  rownames(goi_AM) <- paste0("AM_",rownames(goi_AM))
  rownames(goi_VM) <- paste0("VM_",rownames(goi_VM))

  ## Transpose & Melt for easier plotting:
  df_lin_means <- t(rbind(goi_AM, goi_VM))
  
  RA_means_list[[i]] <- df_lin_means
  plotdf_means <- melt(df_lin_means)
  colnames(plotdf_means) <- c("Timepoint","Lineage","Expression")
  plotdf_means <- plotdf_means[plotdf_means$Timepoint %in% c("d4","d5","d8","d14"),]
  RA_plotdf_list[[i]] <- plotdf_means

  ## Generate mean and standard deviation / standard error
  plot_sdmeans <- plotdf_means %>%
    #gather(Timepoint, Lineage, Expression) %>%
    separate(Lineage, c("Lineage","Gene")) %>%
    group_by(Timepoint, Lineage) %>%
    summarise(mExpression = mean(Expression),sdExpression = se(Expression))
  
  #plot_sdmeans <- plot_sdmeans[!is.na(plot_sdmeans$mExpression),]

  ## Storing boundaries of Standard deviation / Standard error in df
  plot_sdmeans$lower <- (plot_sdmeans$mExpression-plot_sdmeans$sdExpression)
  plot_sdmeans$upper <- (plot_sdmeans$mExpression+plot_sdmeans$sdExpression)
  
  #plot_sdmeans <- as_tibble(plot_sdmeans)
  
  # remove timepoint only present in VM:
  plot_sdmeans <- plot_sdmeans[!grepl("d18", plot_sdmeans$Timepoint),]
  RA_means_list[[i]] <- plot_sdmeans
  print(plot_sdmeans)
  
  eb <- aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill = Lineage)
  
  plot_sdmeans$Timepoint <- factor(plot_sdmeans$Timepoint, levels = unique(plot_sdmeans$Timepoint), ordered = TRUE)
  
  if (subset_nr == 3){
    g1 <- ggplot(plot_sdmeans, aes(x=Timepoint, y = mExpression, color = Lineage, group = Lineage)) + 
  geom_line(aes(group = Lineage), size = line_thickness) +
  #scale_color_manual(values = c("darkred","darkblue")) +
  #scale_color_manual(values = c("#4A1C1C","#943838")) + ## Brown orange colors from well images
  scale_color_manual(values = c("#F33021","#0564FF")) + 
  geom_ribbon(eb, alpha=0.4, size = line_thickness) + 
  #scale_fill_manual(values = c("red","blue")) +
  #scale_fill_manual(values = c("#923838","#EA5354")) + ## Brown orange colors from well images
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("#F7766D","#619CFF")) +
  ggtitle(paste0(i)) +
  scale_x_discrete(expand = c(0.02,0.02)) + 
  ylab("Mean Expression (SE)") + xlab("Timepoint in days") + theme_classic(base_size = 18) 
  } else {
    g1 <- ggplot(plot_sdmeans, aes(x=Timepoint, y = mExpression, color = Lineage, group = Lineage)) + 
  geom_line(aes(group = Lineage), size = line_thickness) +
  #scale_color_manual(values = c("darkred","darkblue")) +
  #scale_color_manual(values = c("#4A1C1C","#943838")) +  ## Brown orange colors from well images
  scale_color_manual(values = c("#F33021","#0564FF")) + 
  geom_ribbon(eb, alpha=0.4, size = line_thickness) + 
  #scale_fill_manual(values = c("red","blue")) +
  #scale_fill_manual(values = c("#923838","#EA5354")) + ## Brown orange colors from well images
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("#F7766D","#619CFF")) +
  ggtitle(paste0(i)) +
  scale_x_discrete(expand = c(0.02,0.02)) + 
  ylab("Mean Expression (SE)") + xlab("Timepoint in days") + theme_classic(base_size = 18) + NoLegend()    
  }
  subset_nr <- subset_nr + 1
  
  
  
  ggplot_list[[i]] <- g1
}
